; Brute: a big, slow melee enemy that SWINGS a weapon in a telegraphed arc (vs the goblin's lunge).
; Has reach + hits hard, but the swing direction locks on the wind-up — sidestep the cone to dodge.
; Inherits BaseEnemy (swing attack via AIComponent.swing).

